These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, comedy, horror, western, drama
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: punk, electronic, d&b, rock, metal
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
5. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
6. the person watching action movies is in the middle##1
7. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | horror | action | drama | western |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | punk | d&b     | rock       | electronic  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, water, lemonade, mirinda, 7up
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, trance, folk, country, funk
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
5. the person drinking water is the fan of folk##1
6. the fan of funk is the person drinking 7up##1
7. the fan of country is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Beverage      | water | lemonade | cola | mirinda | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | country   | house       | trance    | funk   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
There 5 different types of food: pumpkin, lemon, potato, cranberry, radish
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, car, van, roller
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the person eating potato is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the car##1
6. the person eating lemon is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food        | potato | cranberry | lemon | pumpkin | radish |
| Transport   | quad-bike  | motorbike      | roller | car | van      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: rock-climbing, puzzles, skydiving, magic-tricks, chess
The people have 5 different jobs:  electrician, mechanic, project-manager, software-developer, dancer
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the mechanic##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the mechanic##1
3. the software-developer is on the right of the electrician##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the dancer##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the project-manager is on the far right##1
7. the dancer is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks    | rock-climbing        | skydiving | puzzles | chess |
| Job     | electrician | software-developer | dancer  | mechanic   | project-manager |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: asparagus, peach, raspberry, potato, blueberry
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, baseball, sailing, skiing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the person eating blueberry##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person eating potato##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Food    | raspberry   | asparagus     | peach   | potato         | blueberry |
| Sport   | cricket | skiing | sailing | skateboarding | baseball     |

