.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, lacrosse, basketball, climbing, snowboarding
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, scooter, airplane, trike
1. the person driving the airplane is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Sport       | climbing   | basketball   | lacrosse | snowboarding | swimming |
| Transport   | snowmobile | scooter | airplane   | trike | bus       |

