.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
5 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goat, bird, hamster
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: volleyball, snowboarding, soccer, climbing, lacrosse
1. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Pet     | ferret   | goat  | hamster      | dog | bird     |
| Sport   | climbing | soccer | snowboarding | volleyball   | lacrosse |

