2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the dressmaker is on the right of the coach##1
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Job     | coach | dressmaker       | entrepreneur | pilot | security-guard    |
| Sport   | lacrosse   | rowing | biathlon  | handball     | weightlifting |

