.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: filmmaking, electronic-climbing, cooking, writing, skydiving
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: metal, techno, hip-hop, r&b, electronic
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's hobby is electronic-climbing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of techno##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the fan of techno##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Hobby         | writing | filmmaking | cooking | skydiving | electronic-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | r&b   | electronic         | techno   | metal   |

