2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the german##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the russian##1
4. the australian is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the owner of the ferret is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the goat is on the left of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Nationality   | mexican | australian | malaysian | german | russian |
| Pet           | pony      | hedgehog    | ferret  | goat     | lizard     |

