2. the owner of the hamster is the person eating spinach##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person eating potato is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
6. the person eating tomato is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| Food   | spinach | potato  | pineapple | strawberry | tomato |
| Pet    | hamster    | turtle | guinea-pig   | lizard       | mouse        |

