4. the person eating raspberry is on the far right##1
5. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Food    | kiwi | avocado          | lime    | lemon | raspberry  |
| Sport   | basketball  | rugby | climbing | soccer | volleyball |

