.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, colombian, british, american, japanese
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, skateboard, airplane, bike
1. the colombian is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is the argentine##1
4. the japanese is the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the argentine##1
6. the american is in the middle##1
7. the american is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Nationality   | british | argentine      | american | colombian | japanese |
| Transport     | airplane  | jet-ski | boat     | bike     | skateboard  |

