.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-16::.
There 5 different types of food: cauliflower, watermelon, grapefruit, apple, cherry
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, cooking, magic-tricks, gardening, fishing
1. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person eating apple is on the far right##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |      5      |
| Food    | watermelon   | grapefruit | cherry      | cauliflower | apple        |
| Hobby   | fishing | baking     | magic-tricks | cooking | gardening |

