.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, disaster, western, epic, martial-arts
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, water-polo, ice-hockey, climbing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is climbing is in the middle##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | epic  | scientific | martial-arts | western  |
| Sport         | parkour | ice-hockey | climbing  | soccer    | water-polo |

