.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, juice, cola, coffee
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, baseball, biathlon, volleyball, golf
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage   | coffee     | juice       | soy-milk     | water  | cola  |
| Sport      | volleyball | parkour | baseball | golf | biathlon |

