.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: comedy, spy, epic, disaster, mystery
5 different pets are kept: pony, bird, dog, goldfish, horse
1. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | mystery | epic | comedy | disaster |
| Pet           | horse | goldfish  | bird    | pony  | dog   |

 